Additional install info for ETreco.

If you wish to install from a checkout of the GitHub repo, you additionally need the Autotools:

autoconf: http://www.gnu.org/software/autoconf/
automake: http://www.gnu.org/software/automake/

On the top level of the tree, run `automake --add-missing' and `autoreconf [--force]' to generate the
missing links and scripts. Then proceed with the regular INSTALL.
